snippet.title: Let's Talk Mental Health with Amber Reed
snippet.description:
This pandemic has caused people to feel high levels of stress, burnout, anxiety, and depression. This workshop, led by qualified mental health professional, Amber Reed, will focus on how to identify when mental health challenges may be present, and several resources that are available for obtaining help.
Read Amber's Full Bio here: https://healthyuncg.wp.uncg.edu/meet-the-healthyuncg-coaches/
https://balancedenergies.live/
